        "description": "在5 MPa初始氢压和160°C条件下，使用Ni10%/MPYZ催化剂，在正己烷溶剂中对油泥提取物(EPOS)进行催化加氢转化18小时。反应将烯烃、芳烃和杂原子化合物转化为链烷烃和环烷烃。",
        "text_snippet": "In a typical CHC procedure, 20 mL n-hexane, 0.1 g EPOS, and 0.1 g Ni10%/MPYZ were fed into a miniature autoclave. After purging residual air in the autoclave with N2, the autoclave was pressurized with H2 to 5 MPa and subsequently heated to 160 °C at 15–20 °C min⁻¹ for 18 h with stirring at 300 rpm.",
